    <item>
      <title>美国机构称俄罗斯正在乌克兰使用朝鲜导弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/russia-is-using-north-korean-missiles-in-ukraine-us-agency-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防情报局在一份报告称，俄罗斯向乌克兰东北部军队发射了朝鲜提供的弹道导弹，这为美国两个对手之间的军事联盟不断加深提供了新的证据。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/russia-is-using-north-korean-missiles-in-ukraine-us-agency-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:56:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>唐纳德·特朗普在封口费案中被判所有罪名成立</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-says-it-has-reached-a-verdict-in-hush-money-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[纽约陪审团在封口费审判中裁定唐纳德·特朗普犯有多项重罪，使他成为第一位被判有罪的美国前总统。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-says-it-has-reached-a-verdict-in-hush-money-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:39:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>18 年来首次电视辩论是奥尔班领导下的匈牙利发生变革的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/first-tv-debate-in-18-years-is-sign-of-change-in-orban-s-hungary</link>
      <description><![CDATA[下个月举行的欧洲议会选举候选人举行了该国 18 年来的首次电视辩论，总理维克托·奥尔班 (Viktor Orban) 领导的执政党在政府控制的国家电视台上陷入守势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/first-tv-debate-in-18-years-is-sign-of-change-in-orban-s-hungary</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:32:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登允许乌克兰使用美国武器打击部分俄罗斯目标</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-allows-ukraine-to-hit-some-russia-targets-with-us-weapons</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登将允许乌克兰向俄罗斯有限区域内的军事目标发射美国提供的弹药，以克服人们对此类举动可能引发与西方更大规模战争的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-allows-ukraine-to-hit-some-russia-targets-with-us-weapons</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 20:31:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>波洛兹敦促加拿大在即将到来的美墨贸易谈判中取得进展</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/poloz-urges-canada-to-get-ahead-of-looming-us-mexico-trade-talks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大前央行行长警告称，鉴于加拿大是北美自由贸易协定的次要合作伙伴，加拿大需要对即将进行的该协定审查“超级积极主动”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/poloz-urges-canada-to-get-ahead-of-looming-us-mexico-trade-talks</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:54:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登准备发布新命令，加强边境庇护程序</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-readying-new-order-to-tighten-asylum-process-at-border</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总统乔·拜登计划最早于周二签署行政命令，加强美墨边境措施，以遏制庇护寻求者的涌入，因为这已成为 11 月大选前的一项重大政治负担。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/biden-readying-new-order-to-tighten-asylum-process-at-border</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:34:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>比尔·阿克曼在支持不大可能获胜的候选人后，可能会支持特朗普</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/bill-ackman-is-likely-to-endorse-donald-trump-after-backing-longshot-candidates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据一位了解亿万富翁投资者比尔·阿克曼想法的人士透露，他很可能会在 11 月的选举中支持唐纳德·特朗普。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/bill-ackman-is-likely-to-endorse-donald-trump-after-backing-longshot-candidates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 19:03:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普陪审团重新审理小报如何掩盖故事</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-re-hears-account-of-how-tabloid-buried-model-s-story</link>
      <description><![CDATA[将决定唐纳德·特朗普命运的纽约陪审团于周四开始了第二天的审议，再次听取了有关《国家询问报》出版商如何“撤下”关于特朗普的负面报道的证词。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/trump-jury-re-hears-account-of-how-tabloid-buried-model-s-story</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 15:28:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>投资者对南非联合政府组合感到担忧，兰特下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-african-rand-drops-as-election-forecast-shows-anc-decline</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非投资者原本预计选举结果将是执政的非洲人国民大会 (ANC) 能与一个较小党派联合执政。但有预测暗示 ANC 支持率将大幅下降，这打乱了投资者的预期，并引发了一系列不确定性。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-30/south-african-rand-drops-as-election-forecast-shows-anc-decline</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 30 May 2024 06:59:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
